### What problem does this feature solve?
Is it possible to set a custom fallback(404 error page) to separate route group which will be different from the global 404 of the vue-router, If it is please how can I achieve this I am trying to build something like that?

### What does the proposed API look like?
I have used something like that in laravel which server as a fallback if the requested route is not found within a certain route group for example if i am the route group like setting, it might have account setting, image setting, so if for example there is an error, easily it can display like a custom 404 page for that route group

```
Route::fallback(function(){
    return 'whatever you want to show';
});
```

